<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.6">
<l>empirā ṉentai yeṉṉuṭaic cuṟṟa</l>
<l>meṉakkara ceṉṉuṭai vāṇāḷ</l>
<l>ampiṉā larakkar verukkoḷa nerukki</l>
<l>yavaruyir cekuttavem maṇṇal</l>
<l>vampulāñ cōlai māmatiḷ tañcai</l>
<l>māmaṇik kōyilē vaṇaṅki</l>
<l>nampikā ḷuyya nāṉkaṇṭu koṇṭēṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our Lord, our father, our dear friend, king to us, our ruling warrior,</l>
<l>Our leader who, attacking the demons with arrows to instill dread,</l>
<l rend="indent">ended their lives,</l>
<l>Bowing [to him] in the great jeweled temple in Tañcai</l>
<l rend="indent">with groves full of ripening fruit and huge walls,</l>
<l>Gentlemen, to be saved, I discovered for myself</l>
<l rend="indent">the name which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
